    "description": "Join the Rapido Consulting Pvt Ltd family as a SEO Specialist in Ludhiana. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Rapido Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nRapido Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rapido Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
